// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1139 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: c8c68412-90d7-5a46-9285-0b7e4b179a49

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:2*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:7*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04-ESM*")
